<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My First Webpage</title>

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: red;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        img {
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 4px solid #007BFF;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <h1>Welcome to My First Webpage</h1>

    <h2>About Me</h2>

    <p>Hello! My name is Jayson. This is my first webpage created using HTML and CSS.</p>

    <img src="myimage.jpg" alt="My Photo">

    <p>
        Visit
        <a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">Google</a>
        to learn more.
    </p>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 My First Webpage | Designed by Jayson</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
